CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fthree separate arson attacks on
OL,8,Fproperties and a car linked to the
OL,9,FPrime Minister, Sir Keir Starmer.
OL,11,FFollowing a trial at the Old Bailey,
OL,12,FRoman Lavrynovych, 22, and Stanislas
OL,13,FCarpiuc were found guilty of
OL,14,Fconspiracy to damage property by fire.
OL,15,FThey will be sentenced on Friday.
OL,17,FLavrynovych was also convicted of two
OL,18,Fcounts of damaging property by fire
OL,19,Fbeing reckless as to whether life is
OL,20,Fendangered.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
