PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FA third man, Petro Pochynok, 35, was
OL,7,Facquitted of conspiracy to damage
OL,8,Fproperty by fire.
OL,10,FThe arson attacks took place in a
OL,11,Fresidential area of north London over
OL,12,Fthree nights in May 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe first took place in the early
OL,7,Fhours of the 8th May 2025 after
OL,8,Fresidents reported that a Toyota RAV4
OL,9,Fwas on fire in Kentish Town.
OL,10,FInitially, the blaze was not thought
OL,11,Fto be suspicious but closer
OL,12,Fexamination revealed that the vehicle
OL,13,Fhad been set alight deliberately using
OL,14,Fa flame on the driver's side front end.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FThree nights later, on the 11th May
OL,7,F2025, a fire was reported at a house
OL,8,Fin Kentish Town. Evidence taken from
OL,9,Fthe scene showed a petroleum
OL,10,Fdistillate, such as white spirit, had
OL,11,Fbeen poured onto the front door of the
OL,12,Faddress and ignited. The fire then
OL,13,Fspread into the hallway of the
OL,14,Fpremises, putting the lives of the
OL,15,Foccupants at risk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe third fire was reported one night
OL,7,Flater, on the 12th May 2025, at a
OL,8,Fhouse in Kentish Town close to where
OL,9,Fthe Toyota RAV4 car had been found
OL,10,Falight. Once again, the fire had been
OL,11,Fstarted deliberately at the front door
OL,12,Fof the address, with the use of white
OL,13,Fspirit or a similar ignitable liquid.
OL,14,FThe fire, and the smoke that it
OL,15,Fproduced, put the occupants of the
OL,16,Fhouse at risk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FDuring the trial, incriminating
OL,7,Fmessages between Lavrynovych and
OL,8,FCarpiuc were recovered from their
OL,9,Fmobile phones and location data placed
OL,10,Fthem near the scenes.
OL,12,FIt was also revealed that Lavrynovych
OL,13,Freturned to photograph the damage,
OL,14,Fsupporting the prosecution's case that
OL,15,Fthe offences were planned rather than
OL,16,Fspontaneous.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, Head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's Special Crime
OL,8,Fand Counter Terrorism Division, said:
OL,9,F"These were deliberate and dangerous
OL,10,Facts of arson, carried out against
OL,11,Fproperties and a vehicle linked to the
OL,12,FPrime Minister, and they posed a
OL,13,Fserious risk to life.
OL,15,F"Such offences go beyond damage to
OL,16,Fproperty ` they are intended to
OL,17,Fintimidate and undermine public
OL,18,Fconfidence, and that will not be
OL,19,Ftolerated.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,F"Today's convictions demonstrate that
OL,7,Fthose who commit criminal acts,
OL,8,Fincluding acts of arson, to pursue
OL,9,Ftheir, or others' agendas, will be
OL,10,Finvestigated thoroughly and prosecuted
OL,11,Frobustly.
OL,13,F"The CPS will continue to work closely
OL,14,Fwith our partners in law enforcement
OL,15,Fto ensure that anyone responsible for
OL,16,Fthis kind of criminal behaviour is
OL,17,Fheld fully accountable."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
