OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1781536274
OL,3,CTwo men convicted of arson attacks
OL,4,Clinked to the Prime Minister
OL,6,FThe prosecution specified that the
OL,7,Fcase did not depend on proving
OL,8,Fpolitical or ideological motivation,
OL,9,Fnor on whether the defendants knew the
OL,10,Fproperties were linked to the Prime
OL,11,FMinister. It was argued that agreeing
OL,12,Fto set fires in residential areas
OL,13,Fnecessarily involved recognising the
OL,14,Frisk to human life.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
